            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>HSK 2 grammar points</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(Redirected from <a href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/?title=HSK_2&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK 2">HSK 2</a>)</span></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><a href="https://amzn.to/2xwBBcN" rel="nofollow"><img alt="HSK2.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/d/d7/HSK2.jpg/800px-HSK2.jpg" decoding="async" width="800" height="534" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/d/d7/HSK2.jpg 1.5x" /></a>
</p><p><b>"HSK 2"</b> is the second level of the <i>Hanyu Shuiping Kaoshi</i> (HSK). There are <b>79</b> total <b>HSK 2 grammar points</b> in the list below. You may also want to <a href="HSK_2_grammar_points_with_CEFR" title="HSK 2 grammar points with CEFR">see the CEFR levels for these HSK grammar points</a>, or refer to our <a href="./Reference:HSK_Standard_Course_2" title="Reference:HSK Standard Course 2">HSK 2 Standard Course textbook index page</a>.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
