<tr>
<td><a href="ASGAQV6C" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGAQV6C">Expressing "everything" with "shenme dou"</a></td>
<td>什么 + 都 / 也⋯⋯</td>
<td><span class="liju">爸爸 <em>什么 都</em> 知道。</span>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="ASGZ8OIF" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGZ8OIF">Expressing "stop doing" with "bie… le"</a></td>
<td>别 + Verb + 了</td>
<td><span class="liju"><em>别</em> 哭 <em>了</em>，烦 死了 。</span>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="ASG0UFR4" class="mw-redirect" title="ASG0UFR4">The "shi... de" construction for indicating purpose</a></td>
<td>是⋯⋯ 的</td>
<td><span class="liju">我 <em>是</em> 来 上海 旅游 <em>的</em> 。</span>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="ASG8YTSF" class="mw-redirect" title="ASG8YTSF">The "shi... de" patterns: an overview</a></td>
<td>是⋯⋯ 的</td>
<td><span class="liju">你 <em>是</em> 哪个 学校 <em>的</em> ？</span>
</td></tr>
</tbody></table><h4><span id="Basic/Simple_Sentence_Patterns"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Basic.2FSimple_Sentence_Patterns">Basic/Simple Sentence Patterns</span></h4>
